
Checkout phpembed/trunk
+++++++++++++++++++++++

(1) Update configure.ac. Change AM_INIT_AUTOMAKE version number. Commit.

(2) Run "make dist"
    // creates a "phpembed-x.y.z.tar.gz" file

(3) Extract contents of tar gzip file. Remove all files / dirs except
    bootstrap.sh  configure.ac  COPYING  docs  examples  LICENSE  Makefile.am  NEWS phpembedVersion.h.in  README  SConstruct  src

(4) Re tar / gzip into a new file named "phpembed-<year><mon><day>.tar.gz

(5) Verify content of tar file. Try a build etc.

(6) Check into svn+ssh://tubbs/svnroot/projects/phpembed

(7) Hand over to Boz / SHire to opensource.
